{"tid":1180453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［懶人包］逃犯條例","createTime":"2019-06-01T00:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T06:41:42.000Z","uid":185066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"10a7a9febc1cbaf295791d13f07afee908cdf1fa","tid":1180453,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T00:02:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/懶人包-逃犯條例-關我咩事/?fbclid=IwAR3VC0shOXLBQ3HB_LNBUYHykRTJ2GZl_4jP_dASQ4MbMz7GkIkV9d8FjtI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%87%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%97%9C%E6%88%91%E5%92%A9%E4%BA%8B%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3VC0shOXLBQ3HB_LNBUYHykRTJ2GZl_4jP_dASQ4MbMz7GkIkV9d8FjtI&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=2d5f3b62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%87%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%97%9C%E6%88%91%E5%92%A9%E4%BA%8B%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3VC0shOXLBQ3HB_LNBUYHykRTJ2GZl_4jP_dASQ4MbMz7GkIkV9d8FjtI&h=1a9db628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/懶人包-逃犯條例-關我咩事/?fbclid=IwAR3VC0shOXLBQ3HB_LNBUYHykRTJ2GZl_4jP_dASQ4MbMz7GkIkV9d8FjtI</a><br />\n<br />\n以上條link概括曬咁多位無知既人所有會問既問題 懶得睇番之前既新聞就禁入去睇下 唔好再話唔關自己事啦 <br />\n<br />\n同埋6月9號最好出黎表態(可能係最後一次) 原則上既野係唔應該退讓 起碼個立場要呈現左俾人睇先 無論結果點都好 有表態同冇表態係差好遠架 即使佢到最後可能都係通過 咁起碼國際見證住大家都盡曬力捍衛自己既人權 可能仲搏到人地幫你呢 你個個都話冇用 唔好話人地幫啦 人地甚至睇你唔起 心唸點解逃犯條例咁大件事你都可以默許 連外國人都幫自己出聲 身為香港人又有咩資格質疑自己既行動冇用呢？你可以話鬼佬幫自己係出於利益 唔理係出於邊個原因 我只係覺得香港人如果on99咁等條例就咁通過真係好羞家囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個個都問遊行完又點 其實我唸每一個人心入面都冇底 應該話都唔會有咩planning 其實又plan得d乜 場遊行會到咩地步 就好睇果日出席人數同用咩抗爭手段 連人都唔夠仲抗咩爭 得幾丁友係度圍威喂plan乜都冇用啦 所以先呼籲大家出席<br />\n<br />\n最後 循例都係要宣傳個美國白宮聯署(記得email verify)<br />\n請大家花一分鐘幫手簽左佢 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=af42c1ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a>"},{"pid":"19a3d15fea2cbe5ab2877535bad1205b24d0ce81","tid":1180453,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">加油</span></span>"}]}